---
title: Mediterranean Chicken & Garlic Almond Crumb with Roast Root Veggie Toss & Capsicum Relish
description: Sure, searing up some plain chicken for dinner is all fine and dandy. But why not take it up a notch with this
aromatic herby crumb that's scatted over the chicken as a crunchy finishing touch? It'll contrast perfectly with the
tangy pesto dressing. Trust us, this is going to be your new chicken dinner.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/648130e738f49a2a03a2f02a-246caa4f.jpeg
